{"tid":625111,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"分心睇女仔　男校生頻寫錯字","createTime":"2018-04-11T07:21:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-11T07:52:05.000Z","uid":72713,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"07b8891bc799d5c8f9028de11b306f3273ed3279","tid":625111,"uid":72713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T07:21:29.000Z","msg":"本報訊】面紅、搓手，通常只會在拍拖約會時出現，料不到連文憑試也有此現象。就讀港島東區男校慈幼英文學校的葉同學，昨在應考中文科時，因鄰座均為女生，令他頓感緊張，頻頻搓手兼寫錯字，影響他考試表現。<br />\n20歲的葉同學，中四曾重讀一年，昨日他在中文科考試後談及應考心情，表示因為座位左右均為女生，雖然家有姊妹，但因為甚少接觸同齡女生，故在應試時分心「睇女仔」。<br />\n女生的存在還令他緊張發冷，忙於「搓手」。記者問他鄰座女生穿甚麼衣服令他分心，他指「普通禦寒衣物」。他和女記者對話時，也有面紅、搓手。他認為若可分開男女生試場，對男生較好。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20140408/18682740\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20140408%2F18682740&d=e9b57mX1U%2F8HESOwWlL%2FBcmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=eea0594e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20140408%2F18682740&h=42aff3bc\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20140408/18682740</a>"},{"pid":"e9566a2d55d11761de4e64bfcb0da996e8e99a72","tid":625111,"uid":28619,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T07:22:26.000Z","msg":"黑絲擾敵法重現江湖！！！！"},{"pid":"a8135298b47ce5937400a7ee8fcfe60d7b022fed","tid":625111,"uid":38293,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T07:23:31.000Z","msg":"毒撚就毒撚啦"},{"pid":"cb287bff2228e8477509e182b24720c47472cca9","tid":625111,"uid":19979,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T07:23:42.000Z","msg":"轉左做聖人mode先去考啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a81e742142cf89d87ee6464c202ae8b722714b9c","tid":625111,"uid":25887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T07:24:01.000Z","msg":"連登仔考試"},{"pid":"1c73da914fa9c9c31e6ea5dd6b5d448555a698bf","tid":625111,"uid":5490